  "name": "Wilting Rose (Greater)",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>This wilted rose is preserved by magic. The spell attack roll of any spell cast by Activating this item is [[/r 1d20+14 #Spell Attack Roll]]{+14}, and the spell DC is 24.</p><ul><li><strong>Armor</strong> You gain resistance 5 to acid and attacks by demons.</li><li><strong>Weapon</strong> After you cast an acid spell by Activating the <em>pickled demon tongue</em>, your Strikes with the weapon deal an additional @Damage[1d6[acid]] damage until end of your next turn.</li></ul><p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.YDyMLCOZR3NmrtEQ]{Effect: Wilting Rose - Armor (Greater)}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.Qt3buDGMOO75GAbu]{Effect: Wilting Rose - Weapon (Greater)}</p><hr /><p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p><p><strong>Effect</strong> You cast @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.gISYsBFby1TiXfBt]{Acid Splash}.</p><hr /><p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p><p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p><p><strong>Effect</strong> You cast 3rd-rank @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.rnNGALRtsjspFTws]{Acidic Burst} (@Check[reflex|dc:24|basic|traits:spell]).</p>"
